query:
SELECT
                id as "id!",
                execution_id as "execution_id!: Uuid",
                output_type,
                content,
                timestamp as "timestamp!: DateTime<Utc>",
                hive_synced_at as "hive_synced_at: DateTime<Utc>"
               FROM log_entries
               WHERE hive_synced_at IS NULL
               ORDER BY execution_id, id ASC
               LIMIT $1
